===Noun===

'''scissors'''

Plural

#a type of cutting tool (also called a ''pair of scissors'') that is held in one hand and  consists of two blades attached at a pivot point in such a way that the blades slide accross each other when the handles are closed. One handle has an opening for fingers and the other has an opening for the thumb. Scissors are used for cutting paper, cloth, hair and similar material. A large pair of scissors may be called ''[[shears]]''.

